<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-PT">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Details | Creative Technologist</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/estilo.min.css">
</head>

<body>

    <main>
        <section class="project-detail-hero">

            <a href="projects.html" class="back-link">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Projects
            </a>

            <div class="project-meta-top">
                <span class="badge-outline">UX/UI</span>
                <span class="dot-separator">•</span>
                <span class="year">2023</span>
            </div>

            <h1>Celfocus Website</h1>

            <p class="project-description">Designed a concept website for Adidas, focused on creating a dynamic and
                engaging digital
                experience that reflects the brand’s energy, innovation, and sporty identity.</p>

            <div class="project-meta-bottom">
                <span><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i> 7 months</span>
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> 2 designers</span>
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-award"></i> UX/UI Design</span>
            </div>

            <div class="project-actions">
                <a href="https://www.celfocus.com/" class="btn-branco">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> View Live
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="project-hero-image">
                <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65363d385688281ce5b016e9/6a2060652f0419659d0bf3d4_celfocus-Fastweb-%20redefining-AIOps-with-predictive-digital%20twins-thumb.jpg"
                    alt="Celfocus Logo" class="capa-detalhe">
            </div>

        </section>

        <section class="project-results-section">
            <div class="project-stats-grid">

                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="numero">100K+</span>
                    <span class="etiqueta">CONTENT</span>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="numero">70%</span>
                    <span class="etiqueta">TIMESAVED</span>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="numero">12</span>
                    <span class="etiqueta">LANGUAGES</span>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="project-challenge-solution">
            <div class="challenge-solution-grid">

                <div class="text-block">
                    <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i> The Challenge</h3>
                    <p>Enterprise digital systems at Celfocus required improved usability and clearer user flows. The
                        main challenge was to simplify complex interfaces and workflows while maintaining functionality,
                        ensuring users could navigate and complete tasks efficiently.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-block">
                    <h3><i class="fa-regular fa-lightbulb"></i> The Solution</h3>
                    <p>We designed a UX/UI concept focused on improving clarity, structure, and usability across
                        enterprise interfaces. The solution prioritizes user-centered design, simplifying complex
                        workflows and introducing more consistent and intuitive interaction patterns.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="project-features-section">
            <div class="features-header">
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <p>Core functionalities that make this project stand out</p>
            </div>

            <ul class="features-grid">

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Simplified enterprise workflows</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Consistent design system usage</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Clear information hierarchy</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Improved navigation structure</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Responsive interface design</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Enhanced usability for complex tasks</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Seamless checkout user flow</span>
                </li>

                <li class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check"></i>
                    <span>Enhanced usability for complex tasks</span>
                </li>

            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="project-impact-section">
            <div class="impact-header">
                <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-trend-up"></i> Results & Impact</h2>
                <p>Measurable outcomes from this project</p>
            </div>

            <ul class="impact-grid">

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Improved task efficiency</p>
                </li>

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Reduced user friction</p>
                </li>

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Increased interface consistency</p>
                </li>

                <li class="impact-item">
                    <p>Stronger usability foundation</p>
                </li>

            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="project-testimonial-section">
            <figure class="testimonial-figure">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left quote-icon"></i>

                <blockquote>
                    <p>The redesigned interface significantly improves clarity and makes complex workflows much easier to navigate. It feels much more intuitive and efficient.</p>
                </blockquote>

                <figcaption>
                    <hr class="separator-line">
                    <strong>Miguel Esteves</strong>
                    <span>Celfocus Client</span>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
        </section>
